It productizes concepts and seed material from the Agentic Product Standard
(Moai Team LLC, MIT — https://github.com/Moai-Team-LLC/agentic-product-standard),
specifically the `templates/security/` red-team & supply-chain kit:
  - lethal_trifecta_check.py  → src/graph/ (toxic-flow graph, TypeScript port)
  - injection_cases.yaml      → attacks/ (attack corpus)
  - pin_mcp_tools.sh          → MCP hash-pin / rug-pull concept

Attack mappings reference the OWASP Top 10 for Agentic Applications (ASI01–ASI10)
and MITRE ATLAS technique identifiers. Those taxonomies are the property of their
respective owners and are referenced for interoperability only.
